== 游戏 ==

* ''[[Undertow_(video_game)|Undertow]]'' (2007)
* ''[[Shadow_Complex|Shadow Complex]]'' (2009)
* ''[[Infinity_Blade|Infinity Blade]]'' (2010)
* ''[[Infinity_Blade_II|Infinity Blade II]]'' (2011)
* ''[[Vote!!!_The_Game|Vote!!! The Game]]'' (2012)
* ''[[Infinity_Blade_III|Infinity Blade III]]'' (2013)
* ''[[Spyjinx|Spyjinx]]'' (2016)

